description:
Wednesday 11/22- Today on the show we went back to our interview with Gary Owen's stopped by and spoke about Kevin Hart owing him money and more. We also revisited the time when Yo Gotti stopped by and spoke about his relationship or non relationship with Young Dolph and more. Moreover, we flashed back the time Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to the owner of a restaurant called "Sweet Dixie Chicks" who was using Popeyes chicken, yet saying she makes her chicken from scratch. Also, we flashed back to the most wildest Ask Yee's, with one listener that needed to be on the "Maury" show instead.
